      <title>memcached的部署与python调用</title>
      <link>https://qianfuxin.gitHub.io/post/memcached%E7%9A%84%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E4%B8%8Epython%E8%B0%83%E7%94%A8/</link>
